    dc:creator "Ivković, Slobodan; Horvat, Laslo; Iorgu, Ștefan" ;
    dc:date "2020" ;
    dc:title "Rediscovery of Southern Barbed-wire Bush-cricket, Onconotus servillei Fischer von Waldheim (Orthoptera: Tettigoniidae: Tettigoniinae: Onconotini) in Serbia, with notes on species’ calling song at the westernmost border of its distribution area" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3667320>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3667322>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3667324> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3667320>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. A—Habitus of Onconotus servillei (male); B—Dorsal view of pronotum; C—Lateral view of pronotum; D—Male 10th tergum. Scale bar 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3667320/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3667322>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. SEM of Onconotus servillei male taxonomically structures of:A—Cercus (Romania); B—Titillator (Romania); C—Stridulatory file (Serbia). Scale bar 300 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3667322/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3667324>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Oscillograms (A–D) and frequency spectrum (E) of calling song of Onconotus servillei: A, C—male fromVajuga (Serbia) 18 VII 2019, air temperature 24°C; B, D—male from Pâclele muddy volcanoes (Romania) 23 VI 2014, air temperature 25°C; E—male from from Vajuga (Serbia). Blue—one group of sylalbles (echeme); red—opening hemisyllable; green—closing hemisyllable." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3667324/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

